pr_title: feat(nirjas): Add continuous single line as multiline & bug fixes
pr_body:
# Description

Earlier continuous single-line comments were taken as separate single-line comments but they actually make a multiline comment in a sequence.

- Earlier :

```sh
# Line 1
# Line 2
code
code
# Line 5
```
Here Line 1 & Line 2 were taken as two single-line comments but they are commented sequentially which might fall into the multiline comment section.

# Solution

Introduced one new section named `cont_single_line_comment`

```json
"cont_single_line_comment": [
            {
                "start_line": 1,
                "end_line": 2,
                "comment": " Line 1 Line 2"
            }
```

pr_title: feat(Nirjas): Replace code comment extractor with Nirjas
pr_body:
# Description

- Added [Nirjas](https://github.com/fossology/nirjas) for code comment extraction. [Nirjas](https://github.com/fossology/nirjas) was created under FOSSology primarily to replace the existing code comment extractor
- It extracts and passes only the license part out of all comments to atarashi
- Evaluator file is fixed and updated
- Evaluator TestFiles are zipped and during the testing, it will be unzipped and zipped again
- .gitignore file is added
